Sataṃ sahassānaṃ nirabbudānaṃ, 
Chattiṃsatī pañca ca abbudāni; 
Yamariyagarahī nirayaṃ upeti, 
Vācaṃ manañca paṇidhāya pāpakan”ti. 
Tatiyaṃ. 
